data.description: Looking for a move in ready, welcoming place to call home? Look no further than this 3BR/1BA ranch! WLB school district, no rear neighbors, large fenced in back yard with a back deck great for entertaining. Inside you will be welcomed by a living room with ample natural light, from there you will enter the kitchen/dining room with a wood burning fireplace, a kitchen with stainless steel appliances and an island. Laundry/utility room with great storage. Down the hall from the living room are 3 nice sized bedrooms and a full bath. Updates include new gutters on garage and back of house, new carpet in master, new hot water heater installed and fresh paint. Call your agent of choice to schedule your showing today!
